latestPosts.caption:
I have had so many new clients and bookings!🥹 …Thank you for trusting me with your wardrobe!🫶🏼

I thought I’d share my updated online styling services and a little bit more on how it works, just as a little reminder in case you are interested. 

After you have chosen the service you require, I will send out a short questionnaire to get a full understanding of you, your current style and what you would like to achieve! As this is not my full time career, I usually work to a 7-10 day turnaround between receiving back the questionnaire and sending the digital look book. However, if you are needing something sooner, I will always try to accommodate where possible. 

If you have any questions regarding my services, please pop me an email ☺️x
